metadata.description:
Vercanus
A red and black foundation on a white background, with fragments of orange and yellow representing the underlying intensity.

Symbol from the art of Magick. 
Ars Vercanus: a system of core magickal techniques and theories. Enhanced perception of reality, expanded consciousness, mastering of internal energies.
